reviewText: James Scott is to die for ... literally! This short film says a lot in a little time. Thought provoking on the difference between the fantasies and realities of love.
i really love that movie it's short (6 min) but totally worth it if you love films ...didnt know Alyshia Ochse before and looking forward to her next project...james scott is wonderful in it ...
What a beautiful short film.  Watched over and over again,  An intellectually challenging film. Love James Scott.
